data.description: Located on a canal with endless views is this well maintained 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in the small neighborhood of Highland Bayou Estates just north of Bayou Vista. An oversized 1 car garage provides space for protected parking or storage. There is also plenty of space under the home for parking & entertaining. A balcony on the back of the home overlooks the canal & runs from one end of the home to the other with access to the living room & primary bedroom suite. Inside is a bright, open floorplan with a spacious kitchen, living room with beautiful laminate wood floors, large laundry room off of the kitchen & a split plan with 3 spacious bedrooms & 2 full sized bathrooms. The neighborhood provides a community water well & the home has a private septic system. With low, assumable flood insurance and an elevation certificate this makes waterfront living affordable! You won't want to miss this home and the opportunity to be living waterside so make your appointment to see it today!
